Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}查克 工作找得怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我找到一个 不是特别喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我在一家生物实验室做门房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他们做DNA试验 制造变种病毒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我看这个工作挺不错的   - 我也说不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}弄得我有一点紧张 到处飘着奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 别担心 肯定安全   - 绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他们会处理得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你说得对 看来我多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我感觉好多了 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}多保重 查克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFKai-SB\fs14\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}《干杯酒吧》\N第一季第22集 "摊牌(下集)"
Dialogue: 4,0:01:28.86,0:01:33.47,Default,,0180,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\fs16\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}中文字幕译制\Na7l9x1jl6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有趣 有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆哥哥的电话 他马上就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他全方位胜过我 他完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 好美的嗓音 谁唱的？  - 你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你哥哥真是个美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他给了找了一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}诺姆 快来 他要给大家表演踢踏舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他在教我学西班牙语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你觉得黛安喜欢德雷克吗？\N- 我哪知道 我在体育课上帮你传个纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他也只是一个平常之辈 在希腊神话里随处可见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}德雷克邀请我今晚飞去"玛莎葡萄园岛"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}坐飞机还是坐他背上？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你和我哥德雷克做什么我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 人家其实想陪你   - 什么？你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我什么也没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}黛安会不会爱上山姆的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}山姆会不会伤心难过？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}诺姆的新工作是否开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}教练是否会去委内瑞拉重执教鞭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs17\bord1\shad1}卡尔亚斯琛斯基会不会来"干杯"\N点一杯"喷火"啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 很显然 我们引发了一个哲学上的僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如同树木在森林里倒下的论题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}树木在森林里倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这个论题是 如果一棵树在森林里倒下 而没有人听到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那么它会发出声响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果那里没有人 你怎会知道它倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我们假设它倒了   - 可实际上不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那好 我昨天去森林 看见那棵树倒在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也可能是海狸啃的 轻轻地落在了地上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你可把我给问住啦 再来杯啤酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}克里夫 你惊到我了 你今晚根本不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我在复习笔记、为我们这次谈话做准备的时候睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你也做笔记啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 今天黛安去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}今天她休息 一定是和德雷克出去玩了\N她每天都和德雷克出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我烦死了满耳朵都是她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}自从那个染发狂来了之后 吸引了所有人的关注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没人再看我一眼 没人再关心我卡拉的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}别难过 说句公道话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}人家来之前你也不怎么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆 再次谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}多谢你载我回来 不进来喝一杯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我很想 但是我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}很抱歉我尖叫时喊错了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 大家好   - 嗨 山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}厉害的小山米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}老实交代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你不但幽会一个大美女 这个美女还会开车？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}她开车 我开她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆 我为你骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}姐的那几句屁话你真往心里去了\N很高兴看到你重振雄风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}谢谢 你的话把我从我哥和\N你那个皮包骨同事的破事里解脱了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他俩死哪儿去我都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他俩去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有同学看到他们两个\N在汽车电影院亲亲热热吃快餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}大家下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 诺姆 你好吗？  - 我幸福到了极点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}幸福到了一个叫格陵兰岛的鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你的新工作如何？  - 别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}本人已经不再是"金斯坦、鲍曼和川上联合公司"的雇员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我发现这个所谓的医药企业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是一个冠冕堂皇的贼窟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}一直从事偷税漏税的勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}所以你辞职抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我午餐吃太长 他们把我开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 耿直的汉子   - 你说对了 我怎能不耿直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}阔佬们在偷税漏税
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}最后谁来买单？还不是劳苦大众
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你、我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}还有这间酒吧里所有我愿意当亲人养的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}今天黛安去哪儿了？不会又和德雷克出去玩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你们色迷迷地说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我以前很欣赏本店酒客们机智的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}现在这里却充斥着流言蜚语\N你们每人头上都该顶一只吹风机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我去办公室了   - 好的 山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你们想喝点什么？  - 我要一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我要一小杯雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}雪利酒点得真妙 现在正好是傍晚时分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也请给我一杯雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 两杯雪利酒   - 再来一杯葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 白葡萄酒   - 葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我很多年没喝过葡萄酒了 干甜型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 也给我一份  - 两杯葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你知道我突然想到一个什么有趣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 什么？  - 啤酒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}天知道我多久没喝过一杯啤酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我曾经在一个大热天喝过半杯啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}可今天天气很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那就和小杯威士忌同饮 岂不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\fs14\bord1\shad1\an8\b0}【锅炉制造工】一种鸡尾酒 将小杯威士忌沉入大杯啤酒混饮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}两杯"锅炉制造工" "野火鸡"掺"百威"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我给你们走个结总账   - 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我没有拿到委内瑞拉的工作 他们录用了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 他们不喜欢你的西班牙语？\N- 不 我的西班牙语还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他们不喜欢我的英语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 太可惜了   - 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}又能咋地？(夹杂西班牙语)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 大家好   - 嗨 黛安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你怎么来了？今天你休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我今天只想在有朋友的地方坐一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你待会儿要去那个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 卡拉 今天我实在没心情\N- 你想喝点什么 亲爱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}苏打水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 教练 你从来不休息   - 我星期四休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你每个星期四都工作\N- 是的 不过我会工作得慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 跟我说说 你还好吧？  - 不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 怎么了？  - 是德雷克的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他今天要飞去巴黎 他要我陪他一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他是个极有魅力的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}满足我一切的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我认为他对我也很有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}休息日也不叫人省心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}等一下 黛安 也许这是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 是好事   - 我告诉你为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我看到你和德雷克的第一眼\N我就说: "两人真般配"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那山姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他们兄弟俩自然更般配些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 我问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安啊 你在向一个脑袋上\N挨过无数快球的老头请教问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你真想问我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你觉得我聪明吗？  - 你是我见过的最聪明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我钱黛安才貌双全 和皇上散步也不虚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}还获得过一次索邦大学的全额奖学金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}现在却被一张1米90的泡泡糖集换卡迷住了心窍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你如果屁股酸痛我倒可以帮你一把 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你说的其他的事实在超过我的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 我正在吐露心事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不但是对你 更是对我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也许说出来我的感觉会好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你想当山姆的傍家儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我想济慈会有不同的表达方式... 不过这样说也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 如果你很喜欢山姆 我不懂你为何有顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}德雷克承诺我许多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆给我的只有少年郎的调戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我可不会因为那些留下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果他能承诺我一些别的什么 我都会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 你不了解山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆很内向 他什么感情都藏在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他越在乎什么 就越隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我眼看着他经历了离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}酗酒 职业生涯终结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}可以这样说 他越经受打击 人就越冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你知道吗 我打百分之百的保票\N如果他没有对你流露出一丝爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那么他绝对爱你到发疯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}或者根本不在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 我能说两句吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}当然可以 诺曼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有时候一对有情男女太害怕遭到对方拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}以至于谁都不敢率先跨出第一步 表达自己的真感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你说得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}哥也有浪漫的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我知道我开过很多薇拉的玩笑 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}实际上 如果那女人突然收拾包袱离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我都不知道该说些什么... 当开场白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}好吧！我想除了强制执行议题之外别无他法 山姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}他在办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我要直接告诉他 我要跟他哥哥走 看他怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果他诚实应答 不向我愣充硬汉子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我会留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}但如果他敢和我开任何廉价的玩笑 我绝对走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 说到做到   - 请等一下 黛安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你把自己所有的未来都押在这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}对方的一个回应就能让你改变整个人生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 没错   - 你能不能等我下班后再说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我回头听别人转述
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}教练 你干嘛那样对她说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这是我们一劳永逸地赶走她的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你糊涂啦？  - 糊涂？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这里面一团糨子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你好 黛安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}山姆 令兄德雷克邀请我陪他去欧洲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我是来向你道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}该死 我真不想听到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}来不及在明天的报纸上登招聘广告了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}大家再见喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我走了 我会想念你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}再见 黛安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不好意思 亲爱的 周一之前不面试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}咱们开门见山 我要跟他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}很好 玩得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}如果顺利就会结婚 极有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 不顺利也会结   - 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们会成为马黛安、马德雷夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们会买下整版报纸做广告 标题是"感恩黛德"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这题目一定火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}生小孩！我们要到处生下自己金发碧眼的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 记得提醒他们饭后刷牙   - 我会成为你的嫂子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你过来吃晚饭时会说:\N"嫂嫂摆得一手好餐盘 真乃贤内助"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}吃了你们家饭 我总得夸你两句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我每年都会给你寄圣诞卡 上写"祝小叔圣诞快乐"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}节日也承蒙你们挂念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}贺卡上有我们的全家福\N德雷克和我 孩子们 宠物狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}金毛儿的是你们的小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 这些你都能接受？  - 你开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:16:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我欣喜若狂 再见   - 婚礼上见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我还需要亲吻新娘吗？  - 你明知故问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}就这样啦 大家 天下没有不散的宴席
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}很高兴认识诸位 人生有你们更精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 大家再见   - 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 再见喽   - 你到底走不走啊 快走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不能就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我身上的疣子都比她跑得快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 撞到你哪里了？  - 我的鼻子！进屋要敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你是想出来跟我说话吧 想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 我什么也不想说   - 你想说 想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 快去你的机场   - 说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不说！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你拿台球室的黑板做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 快把心里话说出来 不然叫你好看\N- 别这样 我受不了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我就讨厌这个 快住手 给我住手 放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 好吧 你别走！  - 认真求我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你别闹了   - 我应得的 认真求我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你先放下 把黑板放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}放下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}请留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 凭什么？  - 给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我又没有傻乎乎地憧憬咱俩能有个什么未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 那你到底想要我怎么做？\N- 我想要你告诉我 你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我告诉你我想要什么 我想要知道你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你又来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}听我说 你能不能解释一下这样做的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这答案对我非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你为什么和德雷克交往？  - 因为我更喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}黛安 听我说 这么多年我对哥哥的全部嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}都比不上刚才五分钟我所感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这可能是我们渐入佳境的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也许我们可以亲个嘴什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}有比亲嘴更重要的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}总得有个开始 亲嘴是个良好的开始 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你想亲人家的时候 没必要还发表声明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不是声明 我只是不想搞突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们的初吻 无所谓突不突然 你大可以冲动一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我有冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}没人会在冲动的时候还说: "也许我们可以亲个嘴"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我什么也不说了 直接亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不对 这样也不对头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我可什么也没说 我冲动着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}咱们面对现实吧 现在时机不对 咱们现在过于刻意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你说得对 事情发展得不够水到渠成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也许我们应该跳过亲嘴 直接上床
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}这是我们相识以来最愚蠢的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}同时也是人类有史以来最愚蠢的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}也许这整件事都是一个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 什么整件事？  - 我们想办成的这整件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}每次我们想亲近 总会走歪路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}就算我帅不可当 你又比较饥渴...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}饥渴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}不是 我的意思是 你来这里已经很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}该发生的早就该发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我们是多蠢 总想急于求成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}太好了 我放弃了德雷克 你却跟我说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}别和我提德雷克 你根本不喜欢德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}- 你只是利用他来引我上钩   - 引你上钩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我是你人生最珍贵的礼物 你却愚蠢得意识不到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你开玩笑！你是我人生最悲催的礼物\N你来这里之前 我还是个快乐的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你真的认为你遇见我之前更快乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}那还用说！你以为喜欢上一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}让你恶心的人是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}我可以以此为题写一本书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}开支票的工夫你的嘴巴都闲不住\N实际上你根本无法让自己闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Medium\fs18\bord1\shad1\4a&H78&\b0}你只是想转移话题
